description: Conrad was definitely a little nervous taking on the wild Daniel, but being the adventurous type he is, he was up for the challenge! Daniel tried to ease him into it, but it wasn’t long before the beast came out…and nobody was complaining, especially not Conrad. He asked eagerly, “Are you gonna dominate me?” Daniel went right for it, “Yes!” Needless to say, Conrad’s ass was plowed hard, and he was left begging for more as Daniel drenched him with his crazy loads!
title: Daniel & Conrad: Bareback
